tags.description: Begun in 1762 and completed in 1806, it extends 2,045 feet into the Salem Harbor. At one time, it was home to nearly twenty structures, During the Revolution privateers used the wharf probably more than any other port facility in the colonies.
tags.name: Derby Wharf
